  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of our prospective study is to construct and validate a non-invasive model
      consisting biochemical markers, FibroScan, and radiological parameters for evaluating liver
      fibrosis caused by hepatitis B virus in mainland China.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
